@@ -16,3 +16,9 @@ This slice makes the merged `COO/briefing/**` package visible in the live COO ru
 
 ## Dependency Note
 This slice should run after the freeze-to-admission wiring slice if possible, so the live status surface can read real admission-state truth. It should still degrade gracefully if admission artifacts are not present yet.
+
+## Wiring Decisions
+- The live adapter reads thread/onion truth from `threads/*.json` and phase implementation truth from `docs/phase1/*/implement-plan-state.json`.
+- Finalized-requirement and CTO-admission source families are derived from the live onion thread state so the status surface can stay read-only and avoid new persistence paths.
+- Missing or unreadable source families are surfaced as cross-cutting attention items instead of failing the whole brief.
+- The CLI surface now exposes the live brief on `status`, `/status`, and `--status` without routing that request through the LLM turn loop.
